snippet.title: GoobnBalloons DX Trailer 2!
snippet.description: Goob, Balloons, and Bombastic Bosses! What else could you need?!? GoobnBalloonsDX Will be available on Steam, Itch.io, and Xbox Series S/X in late 2023! Wishlist the game on steam!
